  <display_name>Upgrade Roof Insulation</display_name>
  <description>This measure upgrades all roof constructions by applying a user-specified insulation R-value (R-20, R-30, or R-40).</description>
  <modeler_description>Creates a new single-layer massless construction and applies it to roofs. Uses IP R-value input converted to SI units for simulation.</modeler_description>
